{"word":"Hinnom","slug":"hinnom","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Hinnom</b> <a href=\"#/H2011\">H2011</a> <br/> A valley west and southwest of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=8'>Jos 15:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=18&verse=16'>Jos 18:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=10'>2Ki 23:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=30'>Neh 11:30</a><br/> Children offered in sacrifice in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=3'>2Ch 28:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=33&verse=6'>2Ch 33:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=32'>Jer 7:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=19&verse=2'>Jer 19:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=19&verse=4'>Jer 19:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=19&verse=6'>Jer 19:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=32&verse=35'>Jer 32:35</a><br/> Possibly identical with Valley of Vision<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=22&verse=1'>Isa 22:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=22&verse=5'>Isa 22:5</a><br/><a href='S:Tophet'>Tophet</a>"}]}